;;
    test) cat <<'EOF'
skytest test <mod> — start a drivable gamescope test session (vanilla + one mod;
boots into the base save if present). DETACHED: returns once in-world so you can
drive it with shot/drive/ready, then `skytest stop` to end + restore Data → full.
  <mod>        a Data-shaped folder, or a single .dll/.esp/.esl/.esm file
  --with a,b   extra framework DLLs to pull from the full profile (prefix match)
